Tu[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dampening qua phen[C3:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] Fresnel (KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] cen[C2:RN_AN_EN] if/else stop):
